1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,083
When we entered, there was a prefabricated room

2
00:00:04,167 --> 00:00:05,626
And there was someone at reception

3
00:00:05,667 --> 00:00:10,584
The one who brought us called him and said—We’ve brought this person

4
00:00:10,959 --> 00:00:14,083
The other completed the procedures

5
00:00:14,751 --> 00:00:19,375
Inside, they took our belongings and personal items

6
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:20,751
There was one person inside

7
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:26,667
One or two people would come and put a blindfold over my eyes

8
00:00:27,667 --> 00:00:32,292
And they took me away, and I did not know what my fate would be

9
00:00:33,292 --> 00:00:36,792
Interviewer: Were the people who brought you the same ones who had arrested you?

10
00:00:37,083 --> 00:00:42,167
And were they from Mosul, or from outside Iraq?

11
00:00:42,209 --> 00:00:47,751
There was a person named Mahmoud who worked with them

12
00:00:48,292 --> 00:00:53,584
He was from the Makawi family—his cousin, also named Mahmoud, worked as a tailor

13
00:00:54,334 --> 00:00:55,667
He was the driver

14
00:00:57,250 --> 00:01:01,751
And two others were with him—he brought us and handed us over to this person

15
00:01:03,876 --> 00:01:08,667
Interviewer: Do you mean Mahmoud is from the area?

16
00:01:08,667 --> 00:01:13,209
His cousins are from the area, and he is from the Great Mosque area

17
00:01:13,417 --> 00:01:15,042
And he used to visit his cousins

18
00:01:15,459 --> 00:01:20,876
After that he became a driver for the <i>Hisba</i>

19
00:01:21,334 --> 00:01:22,918
Interviewer: How old was he?

20
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:28,876
Around twenty

21
00:01:29,042 --> 00:01:30,292
Light-skinned

22
00:01:30,834 --> 00:01:33,250
Interviewer: What was his fate? Witness: I don't know

23
00:01:34,042 --> 00:01:37,459
Interviewer: They led you to the room

24
00:01:37,459 --> 00:01:39,667
Interviewer: You did not know where the room was?

25
00:01:39,709 --> 00:01:42,834
I don't know because my eyes were blindfolded—they took me in

26
00:01:43,250 --> 00:01:46,042
Through this corridor, but to where? I don't know
